Note on regulatory content:

This repository contains references to and summaries of Saudi regulatory
frameworks (NCA ECC / CCC / DCC / CSCC / OTCC / TCC, SAMA Cybersecurity
Framework / IT Governance / BCM, CST CCRF, PDPL and related Implementing
Regulations and Personal Data Transfer Regulation, NDMO Standards) and
international standards (ISO/IEC, NIST, IEC). Those names, marks, and
frameworks remain the property of their respective issuing authorities and
standards bodies and are referenced here for descriptive and educational
purposes only. The MIT License above applies to the original text written
by the author of this repository, not to the underlying regulatory or
standards documents themselves.
